It has been painted by airbrushing transparent paints that fade together over a chrome base coat. This isn't just a weapon, it's a conversation piece - Imogen, Arms Dealer In Training

descriptions.value: A strategic rail line cuts through the region, making control of this area critical in opening up supply lines further into Russia. A number of abandoned hamlets are a reminder of what life was like before the hostilities began.

This strategic valley grants access to the provincial capital of Tarin Kowt in the north. As a result forces battle it out for control of this vital supply line. Large fields and narrow roads complicate overland travel, creating choke points and funneling vehicles and infantry into narrow kill-zones.

Combining heavily armed infantry with speedy BTR-80 Armored Personnel Carriers is extremely effective in open terrain where large open plains are typically murder for ground infantry. This Russian Mechanized force is definitely one to be reckoned with.

Originally a band of political dissidents, the insurgents as they have come to be known, started growing at an alarming rate with the intervention of foreign powers in their country. Now they pose a significant threat by holding various strategic corners of the countryside and have even made incursions into more urban environments.
